lass="t m0 x9 h4 y204 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">心，<span class="_ _4"></span>这一辈子中，<span class="_ _6"></span>尽量不要去做危害其他生命的事。<span class="_ _4"></span>若能如</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y205 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">此，<span class="_ _4"></span>就算你的待遇不太好、<span class="_ _6"></span>钱赚得不太多，<span class="_ _4"></span>至少也会心安理</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y206 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">得，生活过得比较清净。 </div><div class="t m0 x23 h4 y207 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">当然，<span class="_ _4"></span>完全清净的话，<span class="_ _6"></span>对凡夫人来讲也不太可能。<span class="_ _4"></span>毕竟</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
